Headers:
	# Level 1	bold & double height & high pitch
	## Level 2	double height & high pitch
	### Level 3	bold & high pitch
   #### Level 4 high pitch

Horizontal rule:
	---- -> hor rule.

Emphasis:
	*x* or _x_ italics
	**x** or __x__ bold

Lists:
	+ or - -> symbol #7 & indentation
	1. -> <listnumber>. & indentation

Images:
	![alt text](path/to/img.jpg)

Verbatim:
	`x` -> do not interpret symbols

Escape characters:
	The following characters needs to be escaped with \ to be printed:
		\   backslash
		`   backtick
		*   asterisk
		_   underscore
		{}  curly braces
		[]  square brackets
		()  parentheses
		#   hash mark
		+   plus sign
		-   minus sign (hyphen)
		.   dot
		!   exclamation mark	
